com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.errors

Class WZStreamingError

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.errors.WZError
      • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.errors.WZStreamingError

  • public class WZStreamingError
extends WZError
    The error code identifiers for errors generated by the streaming-related API classes. Errors are normally reported as part of the WZStatus object returned by many of the API methods.
